Running Python code interactively: # Extract more pages to find the PUCT formula and MCTS details
text = ''
for i, page in enumerate(reader.pages[:10]):
    text += page.extract_text() + '\n---PAGE BREAK---\n'

# Try to find the PUCT formula and MCTS section
import re
puct_section = re.findall(r'PUCT.*?(?=\n---PAGE BREAK---|\n\d+\s+)', text, re.DOTALL|re.IGNORECASE)
mcts_section = re.findall(r'MCTS.*?(?=\n---PAGE BREAK---|\n\d+\s+)', text, re.DOTALL|re.IGNORECASE)

# Print the most relevant section
print((puct_section + mcts_section)[:1])
